article_title: UPS will Benefit from Healthcare Compliant FSLs and Growth in the U.S. Medical Device Industry

article_metadata.author: Great Speculations

og.description: Given the expected growth in the U.S. medical device industry and the increased demand of manufacturers for timely delivery in order to provide better customer service, we believe that the move will help drive UPS' healthcare logistics business which is a part of its Supply Chain logistics division.
